cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The model's ability to interpret and generate unseen word forms suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the mention of alleviating challenges associated with preprocessing/tokenization suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well.
